        "timestamp": "2023-06-21 17:25:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nHi Fiete,\nJust to add more to Jessica's request: this is probably happening because you downloaded the GlobalJJB submodule at some point, so in order to keep it up to date I recommend you to run \"git submodule update --init\" from the root path of the ci-management repo that way it will sync and stop trying to rollback GlobalJJB to the old local version.",
